Note: The following steps will no longer be required once {{project_name_long}} releases a custom Tor Browser for connecting to alternative networks. <ref>Except in the case of [[YaCy]], which needs internet access.</ref>

Configure [[Tor Browser]] to connect to localhost.

{{mbox
