In Tor Browser:
# Type <code>about:config</code> into the URL bar.
# Press <code>Enter</code>
# Search for <code>network.proxy.no_proxies_on</code>
# Set to <code>0</code>
# Search for <code>network.proxy.allow_hijacking_localhost</code>
# Set to <code>false</code>